<h2 local-id=3D"13fd6fb258ba" id=3D"WelcomegiftforVIPguests(flow)-Overview"=
>Overview</h2>
<p local-id=3D"0187bee37a8d">The <strong>Welcome Gift for VIP Guests</stron=
g> flow automates the process of preparing a special amenity gift for guest=
s arriving today. It runs on a schedule (daily at noon by default), identif=
ies today's eligible arrivals, checks which products from your selected lis=
t are compatible with each reservation's service, creates a task in Mews Op=
erations for your team to manually add those products, and sends an SMS to =
the guest letting them know a gift is waiting for them.</p>
<p local-id=3D"dc2e283c9d9b">This flow is designed to be nearly ready to us=
e out of the box. Most fields come pre-configured with sensible defaults. <=
strong>Only one setting is mandatory before the flow can run:</strong> you =
must select the <strong>Products</strong> you want to offer as gifts in the=
 Get Compatible Products component.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"8718d977-0613-4a71-bb0e-a04c4624ee7b">
<h2 local-id=3D"e2324d0e7ad3" id=3D"WelcomegiftforVIPguests(flow)-BeforeYou=
Start">Before You Start</h2>
<p local-id=3D"7d9a92b3edf1"><strong>Required setup:</strong> Before starti=
ng the flow, you must select at least one product in the <strong>Products</=
strong> dropdown of the <strong>Get Compatible Products</strong> component.=
 These are the products you want to offer as welcome gifts. Without selecti=
ng any products, the component will return empty results and the flow will =
stop =E2=80=94 no tasks will be created and no SMS messages will be sent.</=
p>
<p local-id=3D"7d6522901711">All other settings in the flow come pre-filled=
 with default values and are ready to use. You can customize any of them to=
 match your property's needs =E2=80=94 see the component-by-component break=
down below for details on what can be adjusted.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"94cbb595-e0f3-4f6c-95e2-2f5b1e8488f8">
<h2 local-id=3D"28d042bab69a" id=3D"WelcomegiftforVIPguests(flow)-HowtheFlo=
wWorks">How the Flow Works</h2>
<p local-id=3D"d9b7a648a117">The flow consists of six components connected =
in sequence:</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"6fb69aa7-24c7-461c-a0e7-6dc=
91061a73b" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"4ec98352-1548-442c-bc73-a0711a71e177">
<th data-local-id=3D"03eada8f-081e-474c-93f3-e53b0e103f31" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"a305d2f1d207">Step</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"bfa9870c-178a-448f-b450-9800adcdb81d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"bd383d923563">Component</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"21753247-5e01-4856-b566-1b3147b07447" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"b84ad2df6496">Connects to</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"e2cb0da2-b37c-4bb0-8911-92297edb52c1" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"6ec0a015db11">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"a721ca05-f3e1-48bc-aac4-b2bcaa8747a7">
<td data-local-id=3D"abba4202-354a-4ec3-ba77-63980ce580f2" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"82a0afafb139">1</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e7a2b2e1-df64-42ed-8520-7ae3302dd59b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8917626476d6">Cron Scheduler</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c3195e92-8a62-40a8-8ef4-74bde8bebba3" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d0d1aed041d3">=E2=86=92 Step 2</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"70808b07-9738-4c7e-a2b7-335c0536d8fa" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"32e26c184a5e">Triggers the flow on a recurring schedule (dai=
ly at noon by default).</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"e54af8c5-ea4e-4821-972d-33facea9745d">
<td data-local-id=3D"11522ba1-85b0-4563-b937-8a30422e042b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"97570e977679">2</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"dea34f17-e491-4554-9321-91f21333fb3e" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"82bcba72396e">Get Eligible Arrivals</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e1c14ad3-d3fe-4dcf-a4a7-f506c1047faa" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"62573d553499">=E2=86=92 Step 3</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"0f991013-923f-444d-9cce-bf146f7f2918" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"65eea874fae3">Retrieves confirmed reservations arriving on t=
he target date. Returns a list of Reservation IDs.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"bcb43378-60b7-412a-a8ed-cb02eac6a38a">
<td data-local-id=3D"6764fc41-693e-4324-9bf1-7c9199f8eaba" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"55b15e3fe930">3</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b163e407-b37d-4493-b6d2-90959c148c84" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"727a08403536">Each (Iterator)</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"58510b10-0f88-46eb-b483-c9baafa2d01b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9a56758fa1d0">=E2=86=92 Step 4</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"f1d17be9-0e87-4e67-8544-84fbe8889514" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e6142ecd6b5d">Iterates over the list of Reservation IDs and =
triggers the next step for each reservation individually.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"82836f49-3ae8-4abb-bceb-2ce0a014f552">
<td data-local-id=3D"d2d6a207-c6e0-4307-84f1-e9b5b48a104e" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"911d0322c431">4</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"86ba34ef-0483-4d6c-b66f-334b099cad97" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"dd2023e12fe6">Get Compatible Products</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"5b778d20-d030-401e-b915-af2fba7ad16e" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"87405755414d"><em>Compatible</em> =E2=86=92 Step 5 &amp; Ste=
p 6</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a025c03b-688c-470f-8b59-0bcc6c025be5" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b3e8a7b36701">Checks which of the user-selected products are=
 compatible with the reservation's service. If compatible products are foun=
d, the flow continues. If none are found, the flow stops for that reservati=
on.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"7871cd97-1833-49d8-8b88-6299d78c5b4f">
<td data-local-id=3D"e1f89f18-c65f-4d80-b14d-9451cc3d1b4e" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8cd512583be4">5</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e85d46c3-a480-49a5-9f0c-d05d4012a7f1" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"92cda00c57e6">Add Task</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"83ad5cd3-2d05-4f6c-bb2f-a50d5464cc76" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c8eb7aa98d86"><em>End of branch</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"6489f423-b4e7-4f0a-bd30-821fc22f5380" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6d60450f3a23">Creates a task in Mews Operations for your tea=
m to manually add the eligible products to the reservation.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"88cc5ba9-5b60-471c-a91e-02f105888775">
<td data-local-id=3D"66176ddd-df06-4561-b7c1-1e19a8d80fa4" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"489eaa08ee9e">6</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"90a7070e-bfcf-4438-aa26-691443691dbd" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3aa764802aa0">Send SMS</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e0aec393-1835-4b3d-b74c-4b8495de7377" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"35aaec8ee5a2"><em>End of branch</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"36fcf013-6bcf-4a63-b06d-e5a2303b9206" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f75317acc782">Sends an SMS to the guest informing them that =
a special amenity gift is waiting in their room.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"e5f60e5c6d5e"><strong>Key behavior:</strong> The flow proces=
ses each reservation independently. For each reservation, it checks whether=
 any of the selected products are compatible with the reservation's service=
. If no compatible products are found (either because no products were sele=
cted or because none match the reservation's service), neither the task nor=
 the SMS is triggered for that reservation. This means the flow gracefully =
handles mixed services =E2=80=94 only reservations with matching products r=
eceive the gift workflow.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"7ca034cb-0fff-48cc-900a-c7a027e9c16a">
<h2 local-id=3D"800c26c41bbd" id=3D"WelcomegiftforVIPguests(flow)-Component=
Details">Component Details</h2>
<p local-id=3D"72f3c967608c">Below is a detailed breakdown of each componen=
t in the flow, including which fields are pre-configured and which can be c=
ustomized.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"604df0f3a875" id=3D"WelcomegiftforVIPguests(flow)-1.CronSch=
eduler">1. Cron Scheduler</h3>
<p local-id=3D"e9cf3df0529c">The Cron Scheduler is a time-based trigger tha=
t starts the flow at regular intervals using standard cron syntax.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"fcdef187-49fc-4bc2-a0b6-3fa=
36c57baa6" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"4d14b51a-0b78-417e-8273-204a5c89504f">
<th data-local-id=3D"2a1fab37-2136-4347-abc6-9608231ceb5b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"1ac013e3a0fe">Field</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"358aed55-19d5-4dde-922c-13313948e6fc" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"b1e370ce1234">Default Value</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"b38b8353-7e07-486a-bbd5-fb5709d23eb8" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"3756dd6b2438">Status</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"65307a19-92cb-4908-b6b8-0cd605f9ff1c" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"2c04e6f79d56">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"b84925af-aeeb-486d-8724-8d935bf89e25">
<td data-local-id=3D"e778624c-e20c-4615-bfd3-dadf786c1f3b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2988c99d4d82"><strong>Trigger immediately</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"64891eb2-0a55-402c-bd4d-2adbc4abd1e6" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"16aef9f2cda5"><code>False</code></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ee883004-ba7b-4b82-8693-1e517656174d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ccff42fc1c11"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"t69tmwfzez">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"576cadad-14d7-498c-8c62-9c62232563a4" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"36f615611e47">When set to true, the flow triggers once immed=
iately when started, in addition to the scheduled runs. Default is false =
=E2=80=94 the flow waits until the next scheduled time.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"7d48d2a4-5c2a-4d0a-a4a9-330be2c5a614">
<td data-local-id=3D"c289cf0d-76e3-4d6f-9190-4d143480d366" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3f405a247819"><strong>Minute</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e00058c5-96cf-4b92-8dd4-04387f71d62f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d1426a40ff80"><code>*</code></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"7a4d66d9-cc48-450a-83dc-25f151ee35ac" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"95d09723c56f"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"gwx1e1psyo">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"63d6a76c-61b6-4e43-8d21-e9ec4de54dbd" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"65fa8a950e6e">The minute of the hour to run. <code>*</code> =
means every minute (combined with the Hour setting, it runs at 12:00). Allo=
wed values: <code>*</code>, <code>-</code>, <code>/</code>, <code>0=E2=80=
=9359</code>.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"cd74c99b-a3e5-4fc9-a945-01a29a7779dc">
<td data-local-id=3D"175f38e4-3678-4936-a823-cc48cde12048" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"858cad640971"><strong>Hour</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"144770ef-05d1-4f00-be2d-44ae73ed4eb3" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b3d18fd04e15"><code>12</code></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"1bdd3d93-5774-45b0-986c-52418d025995" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6600988b0aaf"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"nnnux7o44e">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"18259f5e-64e7-4bb9-aed1-558ca962e786" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"57a27ce9ff0b">The hour of the day to run. Set to <code>12</c=
ode> (noon). Allowed values: <code>*</code>, <code>-</code>, <code>/</code>=
, <code>0=E2=80=9323</code>.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"563b6dbe-0605-4324-b769-7efb0040f08e">
<td data-local-id=3D"5dde2812-75cc-4b48-88c6-f4e8969bd159" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"fb6716c31c59"><strong>Day of the Month</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"8ce7e6c2-c761-453b-8e28-cb8754a93dab" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"69c2ee3afd0e"><code>*</code></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"1a2df8d0-a098-44df-b714-86036347c625" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"944c3104bfe7"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"u83lrp0qem">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"50be7120-9cd3-48b0-8a7a-d10631ec6801" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3fa3fa3448ff">Which day(s) of the month to run. <code>*</cod=
e> means every day. Allowed values: <code>*</code>, <code>-</code>, <code>/=
</code>, <code>1=E2=80=9331</code>.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"8646b119-0a83-4ac0-83ed-52af8b407ab3">
<td data-local-id=3D"f67f56a1-68ce-427e-832f-ef4c25d37819" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e93c7fc3c0c1"><strong>Day of the Week</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"811be242-cc25-4c26-ae31-148c20f1a0b2" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b6e0de03601f"><code>*</code></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"743c6054-fce8-431c-9ef6-95226ec3b2da" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e97bdea5612c"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"gwy1tqddqy">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"04e036dd-b3c9-4328-9df3-f47cf343b8e2" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7cf19a92ac20">Which day(s) of the week to run. <code>*</code=
> means every day. Allowed values: <code>*</code>, <code>-</code>, <code>/<=
/code>, <code>0=E2=80=936</code>, <code>SUN=E2=80=93SAT</code>.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"b55d4003-d47a-41ce-b850-7eb118c7832b">
<td data-local-id=3D"be0f8e58-3263-4e6e-b087-1aec91f75485" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d2b5615c9a99"><strong>Timezone</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"29a04b6a-f6b3-4783-a4ba-7986332c5e8a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cb87cc12a9af"><em>Empty</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ed10702f-1e46-43de-ae11-593c99f14dd6" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"04972567f055"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"cyjy6nn8bd">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"06793da2-53b3-481c-ab71-34ae37fd8dc3" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d1df73f20dd0">The timezone for the schedule. When left empty=
, the schedule uses your local time. To use a specific timezone, enter a ti=
mezone identifier (e.g., <code>Europe/Prague</code>). By default it uses GM=
T.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"ff21d1bb2e04"><strong>Default schedule:</strong> The flow is=
 pre-configured to run every day at 12:00 (noon). You can adjust the schedu=
le by changing the cron fields. For example, to run at 8:00 AM, change the =
Hour to <code>8</code>. To run only on weekdays, set Day of the Week to <co=
de>1-5</code> (Monday through Friday). If you want the schedule to run in y=
our local time, leave the Timezone field empty. To run in a specific timezo=
ne, enter the timezone identifier (e.g., <code>Europe/Prague</code>).</p>
<hr local-id=3D"c6f84a1a-e3eb-4345-b999-4a323f1e696b">
<h3 local-id=3D"d1ec5fca7e09" id=3D"WelcomegiftforVIPguests(flow)-2.GetElig=
ibleArrivals">2. Get Eligible Arrivals</h3>
<p local-id=3D"97e61b3d37f4">Retrieves confirmed reservations arriving on t=
he specified date. You can optionally filter guests by loyalty program memb=
ership, behavioral signals (stay frequency, revenue, recency), or rate code=
s to narrow down which reservations are eligible for a welcome gift.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"096f6c4f-23e9-4d9a-afff-83e=
72be0b893" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"6c728077-1190-42df-9bea-a8a91e110777">
<th data-local-id=3D"b216534a-2f02-4001-9680-cb72484ba01b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"646539be6eeb">Field</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"7a185b12-3546-4cde-a521-97abc001350d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"dd55d248e2c5">Default Value</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"c45bfdba-adf3-4bd9-8b4a-6a0cb3f47230" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"557e4e880974">Status</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"06aecf3b-1d6b-4460-bc79-cc9344383018" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"9d7a47a318c0">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"241bb5f4-9ff4-43db-a60c-ce36b3a7b4b7">
<td data-local-id=3D"527b44d1-1cd7-4e2c-b91d-d0003b869888" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b84b40664b2f"><strong>Arrival Date</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4a88853e-a7aa-4a6e-93af-3f1b19eddfb1" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"917ca69b4d6e">Today's date</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"66a90be3-8d56-4931-b215-750ea79bb114" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"053f2278eea9"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"c3m396az4f">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"155f0484-976f-4ef5-9d34-19603fd465d5" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"08f7a3d66971">The date to search for arriving reservations. =
Pre-filled to use the current date so the flow always checks today's arriva=
ls. This can be adjusted if you need to look ahead to a future date.</p></t=
d>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"7fab3450-cacf-4bc5-bf01-91d7aeec1174">
<td data-local-id=3D"bc876600-9805-4efb-822a-e1b6c9c1f168" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"fba2873780cf"><strong>Loyalty Programs</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"1afe668b-7475-4942-93b4-693384f10417" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7c7851e01d4b"><em>None selected</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"f76109a6-2c34-430b-9823-7826e77fe0d9" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5d343e6e8122"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d8d63497-7263-4860-b4c0-deb997f1f252" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b2ecf8b81601">Filter arrivals to guests enrolled in specific=
 loyalty programs. If no programs are selected, loyalty membership is not u=
sed as a filter criterion.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"f73d7c35-3033-4677-b1ab-dcd90ab79b38">
<td data-local-id=3D"7dc29141-c6a6-4b60-9ed5-cd4718765510" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6d2990b9be83"><strong>Loyalty Tiers</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"0372e2d2-e8ac-45ca-aad7-73c8acafa4f5" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"bf9a7bd43127"><em>None selected</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"145af7bd-3dda-4680-9925-db923f15ca0c" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"74f2f29fd581"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"89636abf-5919-420e-89d6-8cf71b35870b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3418f8d44e10">Further narrow the loyalty filter to specific =
tiers within the selected programs (e.g., Gold, Platinum). Only visible aft=
er a loyalty program is selected.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"c7d50c15-0901-418c-8050-ca2b9a807e59">
<td data-local-id=3D"ebd14f75-92fb-4d99-ab03-99b20d593d00" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2c5f90d1c6a9"><strong>Stay Count Threshold</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"7b660d43-396f-496b-bcf8-5ff320d874b2" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"53f6a3711e05"><em>Not set</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"454caba0-1df7-4c50-aef8-5273a46f350c" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6968cb05b4f9"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"72346fd0-d6b9-4cb5-bc31-b31e9f824065" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f715e8770783">Minimum number of past stays a guest must have=
 to qualify. This is a behavioral signal =E2=80=94 guests who do not meet t=
he loyalty criteria can still qualify if they meet all configured behaviora=
l thresholds.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"378e6fd2-50c3-4580-b501-1e9e80b69dde">
<td data-local-id=3D"086a6983-6d61-4d5d-807a-86ce1beb1d64" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"238ef1f56d52"><strong>Revenue Threshold</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c63a8712-15d6-48b1-a01a-6a61f3ad8b3e" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d0e109e88de4"><em>Not set</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a27d4580-d60d-40e2-b74d-5a086a80d14a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b3d4a92f0d76"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"8abf5dcc-b172-4d11-995c-b02f17da4c69" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"813866448a96">Minimum total revenue (in the property's defau=
lt currency) a guest must have generated to qualify.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"ca1a4c68-42a6-4adf-a775-140fd1aaafa3">
<td data-local-id=3D"f1a62eb9-824e-4ef3-8f84-59c1afc4b098" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"90ab1930aa18"><strong>Recency Threshold</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b3de6f80-c569-477e-beb7-0a1cf7fcf42f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"406f0c11c857"><em>Not set</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c919fc91-9369-4413-945a-a146e7ec9063" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9d52c15801e4"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4c6dfbfe-be42-4eb4-8a1c-66aae54a648b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a6311897e52a">Maximum number of days since the guest's most =
recent stay. Guests whose last stay was more recent than this threshold qua=
lify.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"9c94bfe1-118c-4346-8ef0-d105d5ef59d0">
<td data-local-id=3D"d7f42945-b845-43de-87c5-0c0b02acdf97" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"93ce253e8c1f"><strong>Rates</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4c5e1eb7-527e-44ad-a5c6-24f1919b9a23" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c68e38a64b0c"><em>None selected</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ea69993e-fd2b-4a77-a2b1-34f6b9ab0cd4" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6f46307de9c1"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"42c1d559-8931-4c23-bc14-b706c076e0c6" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c05b9c026ac4">Filter reservations by the rate they were book=
ed under. Only reservations matching the selected rates are included.</p></=
td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"68944ae1c471"><strong>Default behavior:</strong> With no loy=
alty, behavioral, or rate filters configured, <strong>all</strong> confirme=
d reservations with an assigned room arriving on the specified date are inc=
luded. You can add filters to target specific guest segments =E2=80=94 for =
example, selecting a loyalty program to limit the welcome gift to loyalty m=
embers only.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"b23bd402-4193-4fa4-ba66-1486b784ce2e">
<h3 local-id=3D"e7a830812978" id=3D"WelcomegiftforVIPguests(flow)-3.Each(It=
erator)">3. Each (Iterator)</h3>
<p local-id=3D"0b601b36fce8">The Each component receives the list of Reserv=
ation IDs from the Get Eligible Arrivals output and iterates over them one =
by one. For each reservation, it triggers the <strong>Get Compatible Produc=
ts</strong> component so that product compatibility is checked individually=
 per reservation.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"ef59ddd2-4bea-42ab-9499-16c=
68ec90ae8" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"5f31901e-b721-49c1-9a30-8651a6272dec">
<th data-local-id=3D"b781c676-241f-4e94-a55c-3a1783c822dd" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"63ad14cca42a">Field</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"f3f5721f-5fa5-4924-8cab-cd62b8ae861b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"9a9df9456aea">Default Value</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"6146c234-1545-42cd-b008-ee28b562a9e2" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"c3fc0895d59c">Status</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"d3b504cb-f0f2-45d2-bdad-c35530a8b2e4" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"1d81deec1012">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"96556f70-2d5a-46d1-90ea-77cb7c1147d1">
<td data-local-id=3D"1ad7d427-4a77-4c9a-a83b-14394718ef23" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9cd6e2dc7fd0"><strong>Field</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a1d7d3ee-e53d-457b-9c65-770ae07dab7f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2e19f130db07">Reservation IDs</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"6176f562-9561-49f3-baab-a0b3cf3407cd" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"31ac0e7a83a4"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"tf013umofd">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"487a29da-685c-4a29-bcaf-af525bc706fa" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"33acd5e540d1">The list to iterate over. Pre-configured to us=
e the Reservation IDs array from the Get Eligible Arrivals component.</p></=
td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"94d9b615-8030-45a6-a69b-4957071d18f2">
<td data-local-id=3D"1f880368-94bc-4125-af6e-10d0db3e4082" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"883f58de289f"><strong>Delay</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"6b2f01d8-252c-4f78-b028-19e9e6953f2c" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d04f387f5aaf"><em>Not set</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"7fdc0d45-f1d3-407a-b9d6-360c74b93c50" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"44c10d225df5"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"236564e9-92c4-46eb-b1d5-c58e423ddd6d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"325863a18fb2">Delay between processing each item, in millise=
conds. Can be used to add a pause between processing reservations if needed=
.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"9ae95e06-4ab9-4be9-8641-ab414a02ac86">
<h3 local-id=3D"e24e2199b108" id=3D"WelcomegiftforVIPguests(flow)-4.GetComp=
atibleProducts">4. Get Compatible Products</h3>
<p local-id=3D"ffeb8acfc29a">Checks which of the selected products are comp=
atible with the current reservation's service. A product is compatible when=
 it belongs to the same service as the reservation, is not a default produc=
t, and is available for employee ordering. The component splits the product=
s into two groups: compatible and incompatible.</p>
<p local-id=3D"c18163b25698"><strong>Required configuration:</strong> You m=
ust select at least one product in the <strong>Products</strong> dropdown b=
efore the flow can run. This is the only mandatory setup step for the entir=
e flow. If no products are selected, the component returns empty results an=
d the downstream steps (Add Task and Send SMS) will not execute.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"0893615a-aece-46fc-8464-304=
955276fcc" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"4b12b1d8-e4b2-4e8e-92b5-d082eaef9fb1">
<th data-local-id=3D"89301558-e710-4643-9c88-e2247f62e05a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"ea25eb8dbde3">Field</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"9a6107a5-222a-45d1-84a6-2911e3fdb677" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"f9818dcdef8d">Default Value</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"d2018dd8-1cd1-4dbb-bc14-5cdffa7e2bca" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"bd445b9c8c40">Status</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"5966c527-5136-48ab-bb7d-0d045d7114ec" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"285e33d5fb56">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"d960ef46-9948-4a69-aad1-b4f7d0c6e679">
<td data-local-id=3D"a9da8286-75f1-4b53-8729-33d646d8fffc" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"69939bbd651a"><strong>Reservation ID</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"44c3e814-8b8d-4189-b52c-f79155ef71a5" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"078f13bd2503"><em>From previous step</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ea41254f-9393-4284-b8dc-04c7b35f79d1" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"10cb45f2cbec"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"la0tydzkat">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"326fada1-8b3a-4286-963a-0528563c6c1c" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0b5dc2de9fde">Automatically populated from the Each iterator=
. Contains the Reservation ID of the current reservation being processed.</=
p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"6db874a6-0bd0-470d-b893-c950475179f7">
<td data-local-id=3D"7c5da8be-f256-40cc-afad-a65e44a7be4b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"28515528ac0c"><strong>Products</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"7b3270b6-da29-45cc-930e-043bf4c23c7e" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7e20804b21dd"><em>None selected</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"8984335d-e72f-4ecc-90a9-ab568650e767" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"df59417d7bfa"><strong>Required</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"926d0df2-572e-4c02-8447-8c090341659d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"890b8ae75349">The products to check for compatibility. Selec=
t the products you want to offer as welcome gifts from the dropdown, which =
is populated with all products configured in your property. If some of the =
selected products do not belong to the same service as the reservation, the=
y will be filtered out automatically =E2=80=94 only matching products will =
proceed to the next steps.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"1fdf13bcf210"><strong>How it connects:</strong> If at least =
one compatible product is found, the flow continues to both <strong>Add Tas=
k</strong> and <strong>Send SMS</strong>. If no products are compatible wit=
h the reservation (e.g., the selected products belong to a different servic=
e), neither step is triggered for that reservation.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"7a4ef506-c391-4f13-9c81-6418aa0a380b">
<h3 local-id=3D"9c052643d1f8" id=3D"WelcomegiftforVIPguests(flow)-5.AddTask=
">5. Add Task</h3>
<p local-id=3D"c06ee78df916">Creates a task in Mews Operations so your team=
 can see which products should be added to the reservation. The task appear=
s in the Mews Operations task list, where a staff member can manually add t=
he recommended products to the guest's reservation.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"7ed89c81-4c4d-4f21-8597-19d=
324cdc98f" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"6ff005d5-9d59-492b-8dad-1b45ecd75409">
<th data-local-id=3D"9a75904d-022f-4f83-b74a-42b1b23e23ac" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"c5493ab1d12b">Field</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"8e549747-bebc-4443-ba2e-90ef12bf1593" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"0ee4b8d948e9">Default Value</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"c6117524-1de1-406b-a990-b965837d9bd4" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"8dcb4fa139f8">Status</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"2fa8c590-43fc-43b8-9f98-9742fe717086" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"e959d8f994ce">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"eb039005-f876-4cdf-b0b8-8237fbf76c4f">
<td data-local-id=3D"bda77f0e-80b0-4b00-9224-686f7b972d79" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"45a6699d8a5c"><strong>Task Name</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"63935f6b-b567-4e07-a0ff-7924f156ca86" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"107fa8e606f8"><em>Pre-filled template</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"52eab721-62d5-4860-9825-916c97f299a4" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3f50b9d7af78"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"coc8s0y3xd">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"1af18584-a110-43ef-9429-6a90ef54ffd3" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c365a76d730f">The name of the task displayed in Mews Operati=
ons. A default name is included. You can customize this to match your prope=
rty's naming conventions.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"8a726e2f-d712-48f8-82ae-82cf27240e8d">
<td data-local-id=3D"55a8642f-9cf4-4557-b202-b895b7802339" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d61a84f1c915"><strong>Description</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"bf7030ab-03ef-4a8d-8f18-69017d848c59" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"290303ca12b1"><em>Pre-filled template</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"791370ab-4139-4fc6-9ffe-a7691d00966c" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"fed5eb503fc1"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"ydd06xwajq">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"5c0d034e-a2f6-458f-9f51-d422ee4d131a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6c7bd2c33cef">The task description includes a sample text sa=
ying "Add the following products to the Reservation:" followed by a comma-s=
eparated list of the compatible product names. This gives your staff a clea=
r list of which products to add. You can customize the description text as =
needed.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"8d056924-0124-4eb6-8558-e27b9bb379d3">
<td data-local-id=3D"d520e710-ece3-463d-b3b3-2ee584d6d0d3" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2b4a978b57de"><strong>Deadline (UTC)</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"35c17556-ec80-470e-955c-2eb03328927c" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"100abceff430">Execution time + 4 hours</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"9cc5238b-0480-443f-890b-e04ffd1bdae0" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"bdd8c23ea12f"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"yxjepp2ky5">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"6ded75bb-bcc7-44eb-bc25-20b2f7ee9941" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"76364223b4f1">The deadline for the task. Set by default to 4=
 hours after the flow execution time, giving your team a reasonable window =
to prepare the gift before or shortly after the guest arrives. You can adju=
st this to a shorter or longer window as needed.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"ce1d4523-f008-449e-9ea4-178bc2cc9635">
<td data-local-id=3D"68b8cfc1-b23c-46b7-94b5-b4eb54e9cd8f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f0360b29aa88"><strong>Reservation ID</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d2fc85c3-a823-41a4-a825-050468f827e7" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b1cf4017270d"><em>From previous step</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c550c535-5c05-44be-a61e-e31b85cc8ae1" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"48d5f50278a0"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"dzmtznkt75">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a1c39a58-8bd0-4883-8bfd-c53240850eaa" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d7467d400923">Automatically populated from the workflow. Lin=
ks the task to the specific reservation so staff can easily find it in Mews=
 Operations.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"30d50c34-4a54-4887-b7ac-3aefd2f6c0da">
<td data-local-id=3D"671fcd48-1013-453c-95ed-0e9cc89f5d76" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"54cf7b9ada65"><strong>Department</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"381d4436-43db-4e8e-b9da-1840d64b732f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"44f076258d99"><em>Not set</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"f7b44095-e367-4881-bb38-27b7e06aab17" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"abc0531631f4"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"01c7132c-a671-48b0-87ed-389b6c274100" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f62aa149ff03">The department to assign the task to. You can =
select a department (e.g., Front Desk, Housekeeping) to route the task to t=
he appropriate team.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"5e111487-c0af-47dd-80f8-84643789056a">
<h3 local-id=3D"6ad272d1aa44" id=3D"WelcomegiftforVIPguests(flow)-6.SendSMS=
">6. Send SMS</h3>
<p local-id=3D"f3512cdf5111">Sends an SMS message to the guest informing th=
em about their welcome gift. The message is sent to the phone number associ=
ated with the guest's profile.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"21c99e53-4b1a-458b-beab-141=
aacda620b" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"be5f6bb9-2bad-4226-8aa8-d8bc9cc67b80">
<th data-local-id=3D"753b8811-df11-4467-92d3-6d31d0e18c73" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"2eb77a611947">Field</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"d41df6a4-9a3c-4253-9e43-fadc31d63975" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"f9cce72bcc3c">Default Value</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"3530dcd4-8a14-49f0-a377-625950e97459" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"9f0b75f7e1a3">Status</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"048dc672-3964-4d45-80bb-b9cf3a3d7593" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"70d18270b41f">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"84bc1845-ff36-4746-9f88-d9bcc521b059">
<td data-local-id=3D"6356c6ee-70e3-40b4-8993-affa3f56c7dc" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5d75e895da9a"><strong>Reservation ID</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"82fd40f3-d27c-4d33-bb60-b0a4a311f450" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"21d2df9b217b"><em>From previous step</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"1bc4cf3a-9e41-420e-97e1-3fe4406bd545" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ae73d8008d9b"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"rbxs2tw4sm">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"bcb8eb2d-e790-471c-9298-96a82ce44837" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6c365531d47c">Automatically populated from the workflow. Use=
d to identify the guest and link the SMS to the reservation.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"8954adbb-c089-46fc-a4bb-4146715af113">
<td data-local-id=3D"67577b05-5b85-41ce-9190-eab72cbe6102" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a832656247b7"><strong>Message body</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ebcb8b2d-5095-445e-926c-4ee20a6424ee" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6aac81fcd5c8"><em>"A special amenity gift is waiting for you=
 in your room. Enjoy your stay!"</em></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"37b3c2bc-e78d-49d3-bd96-43d54b8b99dc" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f6972886d581"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"yurdw3z8ea">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"6908f725-ad76-43e0-8fd8-8552c64de8e9" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"893ab2ca96f4">The text content of the SMS. A default message=
 is included that informs the guest about their welcome gift. You can custo=
mize this message to match your property's tone and branding.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"15f02724-d4d4-4f13-9bf7-3502466750b1">
<td data-local-id=3D"3d69108e-d553-4503-b00f-54e02e208cb8" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a6ebbe403f01"><strong>Sender</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"2759e1a6-9695-4bb9-a9a2-6527b5ec656b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"eae2b303171a">Hotel</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"7e80d354-36ab-40cf-9069-c0bdc450f044" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0821e4645092"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"wsnd58mzbg">Pre-=
filled</span></strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"1218e6fe-8f06-45a9-977c-a27b6c1cf37b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4632a7baafba">Who the message is sent on behalf of. Set to <=
strong>Hotel</strong> by default.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"3edff1aabd87"><strong>Note:</strong> The SMS is sent to the =
phone number associated with the guest's profile. Ensure that guest profile=
s have valid phone numbers for SMS delivery to succeed.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"3e9d1b0e-a42a-4561-9249-6eeb8a2b0e58">
<h2 local-id=3D"fe2a811b0506" id=3D"WelcomegiftforVIPguests(flow)-SetupChec=
klist">Setup Checklist</h2>
<p local-id=3D"6884c898e50f">Use the following checklist to set up the flow=
 before running it for the first time:</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"299f6392-bde4-4f86-a777-e54=
99bb12df4" class=3D"confluenceTable">
