<tr data-local-id=3D"bf1c264a-c94e-4cb8-b9d1-a2a3b647d843">
<td data-local-id=3D"eecca95e-6627-4ad8-a344-3e8db86c8b84" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3fba455935f1">1</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"64faf6d0-cc1f-45f8-8f4e-8023d062fbc3" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3bec0c8f969f"><strong>Required</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"08e762a4-ea00-4770-befb-dec46a63a8ea" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2622d488a3bc"><strong>Select Products</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e191a130-8a68-4a8a-ac16-fa229a4af1d1" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"21868c82da2a">Open the <strong>Get Compatible Products</stro=
ng> component and select the products you want to offer as welcome gifts fr=
om the <strong>Products</strong> dropdown. Choose products that belong to t=
he same service as your accommodation reservations for best results.</p></t=
d>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"623d7565-bebb-4043-bdec-a9f755676a97">
<td data-local-id=3D"773d9ca5-eec0-4750-be69-66ed9853683d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"87f2f7c7f06f">2</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"cd7b61be-c212-4229-bcf9-74418b7bbb9a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ee227e6428d4"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"7e09eeea-2315-4ab5-9b0e-8d640bfb80a9" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1f33adfa92e3">Adjust the schedule</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"bb271f91-0dd0-4457-b4a5-87cf30f35b5b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ce4bebfc2a33">The flow runs daily at 12:00 (noon) by default=
. Modify the <strong>Cron Scheduler</strong> if you prefer a different time=
 or frequency.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"de6dd2b1-d4ac-4980-914e-2acca639134e">
<td data-local-id=3D"1679538d-3229-4956-a36f-3058b2ac92b7" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6ac300c68423">3</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"85bd8a02-be9a-48bf-8976-4b6147d0add1" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3310db018c3a"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"6fac3a1d-9715-488a-b74d-303251676349" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"579627d4470a">Configure guest filters</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d8c99f47-c479-4e07-9f4d-02965786e45a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"56300da420fc">By default, all arriving guests are eligible. =
Add loyalty, behavioral, or rate filters in <strong>Get Eligible Arrivals</=
strong> to target specific guest segments.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"38931000-90da-4f8a-a381-217079630781">
<td data-local-id=3D"a360896d-4ec3-43a3-bfd1-2a7fd296ddc2" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e8639a4abb57">4</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"5d54fe3c-b65e-4d8d-86fd-e2f756161cb8" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7dcd4fe5453b"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"fd785186-35f4-4c4d-85fa-a0fdefb01cf0" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"28aba985f945">Customize task details</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d3b059e5-7be6-492c-9607-e59842137c9e" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3210193b51ac">Edit the task name, description, or deadline i=
n <strong>Add Task</strong> to match your property's workflow. The default =
deadline is 4 hours after execution.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"89773909-7866-4da6-a568-0184ad679cac">
<td data-local-id=3D"9b2c9aba-e6db-4c3f-a51d-b1df271047ef" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b82b78ef84bd">5</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"fc804776-d849-4588-881e-d3790ca4a678" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"871fed3254fa"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"89a7481d-59d9-435c-bc73-fab50f9e197d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f95b16f2d809">Customize SMS message</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"98010499-96d3-464b-86e0-ac5c808bdb08" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3d5db1c96047">Edit the message body in <strong>Send SMS</str=
ong> to match your property's tone and branding.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"3bd4ae76-96c1-4079-9048-5749d254867f">
<h2 local-id=3D"2daaca2eaa31" id=3D"WelcomegiftforVIPguests(flow)-ExampleUs=
eCases">Example Use Cases</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"e496b7e7-151f-45e7-b407-6f88beeb03e3">
<li local-id=3D"d244d0e2-c7e4-4fe6-95d5-b98a3c97abcb">
<p local-id=3D"a97c9910507f"><strong>VIP loyalty welcome package:</strong> =
Configure the Get Eligible Arrivals component to filter by your loyalty pro=
gram and Gold/Platinum tiers. Select premium amenity products (e.g., welcom=
e champagne, chocolate box, fruit basket) in Get Compatible Products. Only =
your top-tier loyalty guests arriving today receive the gift workflow.</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"c2d0bdab-7f72-4041-b013-90c7c829b744">
<p local-id=3D"bd0f36bf8c23"><strong>Returning guest recognition:</strong> =
Use the behavioral signal filters (e.g., at least 3 stays in the last year)=
 to identify returning guests and surprise them with a complimentary amenit=
y, even if they are not enrolled in a loyalty program.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c6609f5b-adad-4aa3-8658-5e30ba53fc96">
<p local-id=3D"39bfafe7d291"><strong>Seasonal welcome gift:</strong> Update=
 the selected products periodically to match the season (e.g., hot chocolat=
e in winter, cold beverages in summer) and adjust the SMS message to reflec=
t the seasonal offering.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2792cf8e-19eb-4106-bdce-376a616beb5a">
<p local-id=3D"2cb90783338a"><strong>Weekday-only gifting:</strong> Modify =
the Cron Scheduler to run only Monday through Friday by setting Day of the =
Week to <code>1-5</code>, reserving the welcome gift program for weekday ar=
rivals.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"0abf8987-4491-46cb-a5b5-ce80c7abc7b1">
<h2 local-id=3D"a3468c5f648c" id=3D"WelcomegiftforVIPguests(flow)-Troublesh=
ooting">Troubleshooting</h2>
<h4 local-id=3D"e258975cf1ed" id=3D"WelcomegiftforVIPguests(flow)-Theflowru=
nsbutnotasksorSMSmessagesarecreated">The flow runs but no tasks or SMS mess=
ages are created</h4>
<ul local-id=3D"b7854e48-bb03-4ffb-b65e-10951d0087a3">
<li local-id=3D"06c47e26-d0be-4537-b7bb-ddf502bf6554">
<p local-id=3D"b16a28704b7d">Check that you have selected at least one prod=
uct in the <strong>Products</strong> dropdown of the <strong>Get Compatible=
 Products</strong> component. Without products selected, the flow stops at =
this step.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d4e27b35-02a0-4d0f-a21f-c2defe829dc9">
<p local-id=3D"56166f76016e">Verify that the selected products belong to th=
e same service as the reservations (e.g., Accommodation). Products from a d=
ifferent service (e.g., Spa) will be classified as incompatible.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f79e99d8-07f1-45fe-8278-cfe32b734c70">
<p local-id=3D"c29f053ddcd4">Ensure there are confirmed reservations with a=
ssigned rooms arriving on the current date.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"45e9c01a-1c4c-4290-9dec-c8d0fc4f8f07">
<p local-id=3D"0aa7d6af35db">If you configured loyalty or behavioral filter=
s in Get Eligible Arrivals, ensure that arriving guests meet the criteria.<=
/p></li>
</ul>
<h4 local-id=3D"6fc931e5bf51" id=3D"WelcomegiftforVIPguests(flow)-Tasksarec=
reatedbutsomereservationsareskipped">Tasks are created but some reservation=
s are skipped</h4>
<p local-id=3D"38753ca25b8a">This is expected behavior. The Get Compatible =
Products component checks each reservation individually. If a reservation's=
 service does not match any of the selected products, that reservation is s=
kipped. This can happen when your property has multiple services (e.g., Acc=
ommodation and Apartments) and the selected products only belong to one of =
them.</p>
<h4 local-id=3D"281cae7548a8" id=3D"WelcomegiftforVIPguests(flow)-SMSmessag=
esarenotdelivered">SMS messages are not delivered</h4>
<ul local-id=3D"e36b03df-1fed-4a54-b8ad-402f73279dd2">
<li local-id=3D"68d84606-541b-4f86-8814-b841ead7bda6">
<p local-id=3D"d10c867017d0">Ensure that the guest profiles have valid phon=
e numbers configured.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9fce02b8-8220-4b84-9d85-c7b2e1300373">
<p local-id=3D"c43b0579628d">Check that SMS messaging is enabled for your p=
roperty.</p></li>
</ul>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
